text: Cobra is a 1925 American drama movie directed by Joseph Henabery and was based on the 1924 play of the same name by Martin Brown. It stars Rudolph Valentino, Nita Naldi, Casson Ferguson, Gertrude Olmstead, Eileen Percy, Claire De Lorez, Harry Barrows, Lillian Langdon and Hector V. Sarno. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1925 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:American silent movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Joseph Henabery
